gsave 8 8 true [8 0 0 -8 0 8] {<AA55AA55AA55AA55>} imagemask grestore
gsave 8 8 true [8 0 0 -8 0 8] {<AA55AA55AA55AA55>} imagemask grestore
count st.c0 eq (a cached stencil leaves the stack clean) assert

% --- internaldict answers its password and refuses others ---
1183615869 internaldict type /dicttype eq
(internaldict answers its password) assert
{ 0 internaldict } stopped (a wrong password is refused) assert
$error /newerror false put clear

